title: Hour 1 – Covino and Rich Guest Host
itunes:title: Hour 1 – Covino and Rich Guest Host
description:
Covino and Rich fill in for Dan Patrick and the crew, and the guys dive right into their morning routines, specifically they share what it takes to be an early bird in the gym. Plus, the guys talk a little baseball and highlight just how bad the Yankees have been in their last twelve games.  Then, the guys want to know if your team is getting blown out, should you still watch?

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
